    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>English:</strong> Sometimes some surprisingly horrible things may happen in children&rsquo;s stories &ndash; I just read about a poor sparrow whose tongue was cut by an old woman for eating her nori. Strange enough the sparrow can still talk after this.</p>

<p><strong>にほんごで:</strong>　したきりのはなしをよんでいる。ばあさはすずめのしたをきった。むごいね。でもするとすずめははなすことができます。どうそうする？</p>
